(65,63,'2013-08-22 18:10:34','2014-02-28 22:21:30','Logitech G27 Racing Wheel',NULL,'A racing wheel from Logitech, compatible with PS2, PS3, and PC.','','','<h2>Overview</h2><p>The Logitech G27 Racing Wheel is compatible with <a href=\"/playstation-2/3045-19/\" data-ref-id=\"3045-19\">PlayStation 2</a>, <a href=\"/playstation-3/3045-35/\" data-ref-id=\"3045-35\">PlayStation 3</a>, and <a href=\"/pc/3045-94/\" data-ref-id=\"3045-94\">PCs</a> running Windows XP or later.</p><h2>Features</h2><ul><li>Force feedback</li><li>Gas, brake and clutch pedals</li><li>H-pattern shifter</li><li>Helical gearing</li><li>Paddle shifters</li><li>RPM/shift indicator LEDs</li><li>900-degree steering</li></ul><h2>System Requirements</h2><h5>Windows 8, Windows 7, Windows Vista, or Windows XP</h5><ul><li>20 MB of available hard disk space</li><li>USB port</li><li>Internet connection for software download</li></ul><h2>Game Compatibility</h2><h4>PS3</h4><ul><li>Burnout Paradise</li><li>Dirt</li><li>Dirt 2</li><li>Dirt 3</li><li>F1 2010</li><li>F1 2011</li><li>F1 2012</li><li>Ferrari Challenge Trofeo Pirelli</li><li>Formula One Championship Edition</li><li>Grand Theft Auto IV</li><li>Gran Turismo HD Concept</li><li>Gran Turismo 5 Prologue 1 2</li><li>Gran Turismo 5 1 2</li><li>Gran Turismo 6</li><li>Initial D Extreme Stage</li><li>Juiced 2: Hot Import Nights</li><li>Midnight Club: Los Angeles</li><li>MotorStorm: Apocalypse</li><li>NASCAR 08</li><li>NASCAR 09</li><li>NASCAR The Game: 2011</li><li>Need for Speed: Carbon</li><li>Need for Speed: Hot Pursuit</li><li>Need for Speed: ProStreet</li><li>Need for Speed: The Run</li><li>Need for Speed: Shift</li><li>Need for Speed: Undercover</li><li>Need for Speed: Most Wanted 2012</li><li>GRID</li><li>Sega Rally Revo</li><li>Shift 2: Unleashed 2</li><li>Sonic &amp; Sega All-Stars Racing</li><li>Stuntman: Ignition</li><li>Superstars V8 Racing</li><li>Supercar Challenge</li><li>Test Drive Unlimited 2</li><li>WRC: FIA World Rally Championship 2010</li><